## 3. `config.py`

```python
import os

API_ID = int(os.getenv("API_ID", "123456"))
API_HASH = os.getenv("API_HASH", "your_api_hash")
BOT_TOKEN = os.getenv("BOT_TOKEN", "your_bot_token")

# Example base URL for Classplus API (replace with actual)
CLASSPLUS_API_BASE = "https://api.classplusapp.com"

# Temporary folder for storing generated HTML files
TMP_DIR = "tmp"
